packageJSON.name: lyricfier
packageJSON.description: Fetching lyrics for spotify desktop client

scripts.dist: npm run dist:linux64 && npm run dist:linux32 && npm run dist:win32 && npm run dist:win64 && npm run dist:mac

releases.name: Fixing connecting errors to spotify
releases.body:
Minor release to fix bugs:
- Loop errors connecting spotify.
- Preventing multiple spamming toastrs messages
- Normalizing common titles (remastered / live / mono...)

releases.name: Improved settings and UI
releases.body:
- UI improvements general/settings by @silvestreh 
- Added settings page by @mrkmndz 
- Added source link to lyrics   @mrkmndz / @emilioastarita

Collaborators in this release: @mrkmndz @silvestreh

releases.name: Loading improvements and fixing minor bugs
releases.body:
- Added loading improvements
- Added fix for icons on mac.
- Fixing bug on detection of http  and https 

thanks to collaborators: 

@mrkmndz  @ThomasPinna @kalber and @jica

releases.name: Dark theme and more
releases.body:
- Added dark theme.
- Added protocol detection for spotify service.
- Merged contributions for MusicMatch plugin.

releases.name: Minor Release
releases.body:
- Added debug lines.
- Cached cover urls
- Fix bug on Always On Top switch
- Changed to `pre-line` by @kcpr

releases.name: Release 0.2.0 improved error handling
releases.body:
- Improved error handling.
- Scroll to top.
- Fix bug on MusicMatch plugin parser.
